nt Unix timestamp. Working backwards from the UTC time of April 15, 2026 at 5:56 AM, I can calculate that it's around 1,776,232,560 seconds since the epoch. Let me verify this is in the right ballpark by checking against the session timestamps.\n\nNow I'm recalculating the 5p Progress Report session more carefully—it's been running for about 2 hours based on the timestamp difference. The DTLX version has been active for roughly 48 minutes, and I'm working through the AHV QLHV Ecosystem session timing as well.\n\nLooking at the final session, it appears to have ended much earlier but is still marked as running in the system. Let me calculate its actual duration: from 1776163408296 to 1776163783190 gives about 374 seconds or roughly 6 minutes of actual runtime, though the status inconsistency is worth noting.\n\nNow I'm compiling the final list of active sessions to report.","thinkingSignature":"ce66352620c7896d0949bd82853c02aeb489de1f755fe80ce891912ab27262c2"},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me compile the status report and send it to Lead.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n3ue96dolhdh_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","message":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 05:56 UTC 15 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 3\n• 5p Progress Report: running — Orchestrating 5p work pipeline — ~2h 01m\n• 5p Progress Report - DTLX: running — DTLX ecosystem progress check — ~48m\n• AHV QLHV Ecosystem (group): running — Telegram group management — ~19h 12m (endedAt set, status=running)\n\nPipeline: Healthy. No blockers detected."}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2494,"output":905,"cacheRead":13849,"cacheWrite":292,"totalTokens":17540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776232614883,"responseId":"062e5ba70410799c99dfceaf73ffe85c"}}
